name: Relief for Feb 05/06 Earthquake in Syria/Turkey

metadata.name: Awakening of Devastation
metadata.description:
Day 37 - Awakening of Devastation by Poke

This piece is dedicated to the Earthquake Relief Fund for Turkey and Syria following the devastating magnitude 7.5 Earthquake that hit the region on Monday 6th Feb 2023. Our thoughts and prayers go out to the victims and families and we hope our efforts can help them recover as best as possible! In times like these, communities like our should unit to support those in the IRL who truly need any and all help they can receive! ♥♥♥

Funds will be donated to the UN Crisis Relief to aid the relief for this crisis - https://crisisrelief.un.org/

Thank you to all who participate!

Poke
